{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so he was ready to kill me, when-- oh, so you are drunk?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So you're not willing to get up, are you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then two of my friends who were still around us and-- and they helped me up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Said, oh, yes, he's-- he's not drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He just slips on a soap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't talk so much, just get ready with your shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had about 30 seconds in the shower, just a bit of water, cleaned a bit of mud away, and out on the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They carried me out, because I-- I was still dazed from the two big blows on my face.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They carried me out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had to stand outside for half an hour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, eventually, we got underpants and singlets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we had to go outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we are not stark naked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had underpants and singlet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we only had to wait until our group is filled up, 300 people in one-- we had to wait a bit, half an hour maybe, [LAUGHS] out in the cold, rubbing ourselves.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, quick running behind me, said the commander of-- our future commander, who was there to pick up our group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to run behind him, which was good-- better than standing in the cold.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went run about half a kilometer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And eventually we arrived to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they gave us the striped pants and the striped jacket-- no food, mind you, still no food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But next day, we got a-- a soup with beetroot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From then on, we had no more cabbage soups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For a while, they had beetroot soup-- a red soup with pieces of beetroot in it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
